/countries.html (controller location countries)
Will list all the countries

Link to big ZIP with world DB


/COUNTRY_SEONAME.html (controller location country)
Lists all the regions of the country
Zip country to download
List of all the region ZIPs to download


/COUNTRY_SEONAME/REGION_SEONAME.html (controller location region)
Breadcrumb
Num of cities.
Cities paginated 500 each
Zip to download that region


---------------------------Zip format------------------
world.zip
world-es_ES.zip
COUNTRY_SEONAME-es_ES.zip
COUNTRY_SEONAME___REGION_SEONAME-es_ES.zip